replies.body:
I may fall into the category of the boy that cried wolf occasionally... because as soon as my enemy is out of sight, I mia ping once... if they've gone for 2-3 minion deaths, i'll mia ping twice... and if they've gone for a bit longer than that, after the double ping, i'll danger ping the other lanes once... on the occasion that I mia ping, and suddenly my enemy laner is in my lane, I have a macro that says: "cancel dat ping on aisle 5 - soz". But I do like to ping, I'll double ping if I see the enemy jungler headed somewhere... making the 2nd ping go in that location... I ping ward locations if I spot it... I ping dragon/baron if all is too quiet and my spider sense tingles... I ping brushes because I'm certain someone is in there... I even ping my mum sometimes. Just to let her know I love her.
But I will never ever. Ever. Spam Ping.
{{summoner:30}}
